No. 51,

Misc.

Dickey v. Florida. John D. Buchanan, Jr., for petitioner. Earl Faircloth, Attorney General of Florida, and George R. Georgieff, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Dist. Ct. App. Fla., 1st Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
